Package: birtir
Title: Render Analysis Scripts and Statistical Descriptions
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Auðun", "Valborgarson", email = "audun@valborgarson.net", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Auðun Valborgarson
Maintainer: Auðun Valborgarson <audun@valborgarson.net>
Description: Runs analysis scripts, captures console output, writes plain
    Markdown reports, and provides report-ready statistical description helpers.
    Exported helpers such as md_table(), md_plot(), and describe_data() can be
    used directly in scripts, printing previews interactively and writing into
    the active report during render_analysis_md().
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Depends:
    R (>= 4.2.0)
Imports:
    cli,
    dplyr,
    fs,
    ggplot2,
    glue,
    knitr,
    rlang,
    tibble,
    utils
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    withr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/auv2/birtir
BugReports: https://github.com/auv2/birtir/issues
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
